URxvt
=====

Installation : apt-get install rxvt-unicode

Files : .Xdefaults > ~/
Perl scripts > /usr/lib/urxvt/perl/

Scripts de lancement
====================

Login Manager LightDM ou GDM :
/usr/share/xsessions/dwm.desktop

Script lancé par dwm.desktop :
~/.startdwm

Conky lancé par le .startdwm :
~/.conkyrc


Simple color Script
===================

#!/bin/bash 
setterm -regtabs 4
COLS="$(xrdb -query| grep -Ei [.*]color[01-9] | sort -n -tr -k2 | tr -d [*[:blank:]])

" echo -en "---------------------------------------------------------------"; 
echo -e "\033[0m"
for i in {0..7}; do echo -en "\e[0;3${i}m▉▉▉▉▉▉▉\t"; done; echo 
for i in {0..7}; do echo -en "\e[0;9${i}m▉▉▉▉▉▉▉\t"; done; echo -e "\033[0m" 
echo -en "---------------------------------------------------------------"; 
echo -e "\033[0m"
